{"applies_to": {"quality_status": ["low_confidence", "invalid", "insufficient"], "scale_code": ["BIG5_OCEAN"], "scope": ["low_quality"]}, "asset_id": "candidate_content_low_quality_safe_to_show_when_low_quality_v0_3", "asset_key": "low_quality_state.safe_to_show_when_low_quality.v0_3", "asset_kind": "content_asset", "asset_layer": "L7_result_state", "asset_type": "result_state", "asset_version": "v0_3", "avoid_when": [{"action": "suppress", "field": "scale_code", "operator": "not_equals", "value": "BIG5_OCEAN"}, {"action": "suppress", "field": "scope", "operator": "not_equals", "value": "low_quality"}], "body_quality": {"body_chars": 198, "cta_chars": 17, "has_action_layer": true, "has_boundary_layer": true, "has_editorial_leakage": false, "has_quality_layer": true, "has_retest_layer": true, "has_state_layer": true, "max_sentence_length": 48, "recalculated_by": "codex_low_quality_candidate_normalize_01", "rendered_preview_required": true, "sentence_count": 7, "short_body_chars": 23, "summary_chars": 24, "template_risk": "low"}, "body_zh": "低置信结果并不是全盘不可读。适合保留的内容，是五个维度的大致轮廓、少量与真实场景相关的观察问题，以及重新作答或继续记录的建议。这些信息能帮助用户开始理解自己，但不会把材料不足的地方包装成精密结论。报告也可以提示哪些模块已被放轻，让用户知道系统在主动降级解释。这样处理比直接隐藏全部内容更友好，也比强行完整展开更负责；核心原则是少做推断，多给观察入口。用户仍能从中获得下一步，而不会被过度解释带偏。", "can_combine_with": ["method_boundary_context", "retest_guidance", "safe_summary_context"], "cannot_combine_with": ["strong_personality_claim", "private_result_details", "ranking_claim", "high_stakes_language"], "copy_role": "degraded_state_policy_candidate", "cta_zh": "只保留能帮助你观察现实行为的部分。", "dedupe_group": "low_quality_state.safe_to_show_when_low_quality", "fallback_allowed": false, "module_key": "module_10_method_privacy", "production_use_allowed": false, "qa_status": "editorial_reviewed", "reading_mode": ["quick", "standard", "deep"], "ready_for_pilot": false, "ready_for_production": false, "ready_for_runtime": false, "render_surface": ["result_page", "pdf"], "repair_log_refs": [], "runtime_use": "staging_only", "safety_level": "degraded", "safety_tags": ["degraded_state", "non_blaming", "bounded_interpretation", "no_high_stakes_claim", "no_external_copy"], "scope": "low_quality", "section_key": "low_quality_state", "selection_priority": 89, "selection_specificity": 89, "short_body_zh": "可以看轮廓、看提醒、看下一步；细节先不要读重。", "slot_key": "low_quality.boundary.safe_to_show", "source_trace": {"bfi_2_copy_used": false, "competitor_copy_used": false, "derived_from": ["06_low_quality_workpack", "scoring_norms_safe_summary", "editorial_handoff_prompt"], "external_copy_used": false, "forbidden_copy_sources_excluded": true, "source_labels": ["citation_only", "structure_reference_only"], "source_pack": "BIG5_LOW_QUALITY_REVISED_V0_3_NORMALIZED", "source_role": "backend_candidate_artifact"}, "summary_zh": "低置信状态下，适合保留大方向、观察题和复测建议。", "target_registry_key": "state_scope_registry", "title_zh": "低置信时可以看什么", "version": "fap.big5.result_page_v2.content_asset_candidate.v0.3.normalized"}
{"applies_to": {"quality_status": ["low_confidence", "invalid", "insufficient"], "scale_code": ["BIG5_OCEAN"], "scope": ["low_quality"]}, "asset_id": "candidate_content_low_quality_should_soften_or_hide_when_low_quality_v0_3", "asset_key": "low_quality_state.should_soften_or_hide_when_low_quality.v0_3", "asset_kind": "content_asset", "asset_layer": "L7_result_state", "asset_type": "result_state", "asset_version": "v0_3", "avoid_when": [{"action": "suppress", "field": "scale_code", "operator": "not_equals", "value": "BIG5_OCEAN"}, {"action": "suppress", "field": "scope", "operator": "not_equals", "value": "low_quality"}], "body_quality": {"body_chars": 195, "cta_chars": 21, "has_action_layer": true, "has_boundary_layer": true, "has_editorial_leakage": false, "has_quality_layer": true, "has_retest_layer": false, "has_state_layer": true, "max_sentence_length": 41, "recalculated_by": "codex_low_quality_candidate_normalize_01", "rendered_preview_required": true, "sentence_count": 6, "short_body_chars": 22, "summary_chars": 27, "template_risk": "low"}, "body_zh": "低置信结果里，最需要放轻的是复杂组合、细分面向、长期画像、公开分享摘要和跨时间对比。它们不是完全不能看，而是不能被写成清晰、稳定、可外传的判断。尤其当报告涉及压力、关系、协作方式时，文字应从“你是什么样”改成“可以观察什么”。这能避免用户把暂时材料当成长期答案，也能避免他人看到简短摘要后产生过度解读。越是会影响他人判断的内容，越应保守处理。这类内容最好留在自读范围内，等材料更稳后再展开。", "can_combine_with": ["method_boundary_context", "retest_guidance", "safe_summary_context"], "cannot_combine_with": ["strong_personality_claim", "private_result_details", "ranking_claim", "high_stakes_language"], "copy_role": "degraded_state_policy_candidate", "cta_zh": "看到较强表述时，先把它改写成一个观察问题。", "dedupe_group": "low_quality_state.should_soften_or_hide_when_low_quality", "fallback_allowed": false, "module_key": "module_10_method_privacy", "production_use_allowed": false, "qa_status": "editorial_reviewed", "reading_mode": ["quick", "standard", "deep"], "ready_for_pilot": false, "ready_for_production": false, "ready_for_runtime": false, "render_surface": ["result_page", "pdf"], "repair_log_refs": [], "runtime_use": "staging_only", "safety_level": "degraded", "safety_tags": ["degraded_state", "non_blaming", "bounded_interpretation", "no_high_stakes_claim", "no_external_copy"], "scope": "low_quality", "section_key": "low_quality_state", "selection_priority": 90, "selection_specificity": 90, "short_body_zh": "组合、细分、对比和分享内容都应比平时更克制。", "slot_key": "low_quality.boundary.should_soften_hide", "source_trace": {"bfi_2_copy_used": false, "competitor_copy_used": false, "derived_from": ["06_low_quality_workpack", "scoring_norms_safe_summary", "editorial_handoff_prompt"], "external_copy_used": false, "forbidden_copy_sources_excluded": true, "source_labels": ["citation_only", "structure_reference_only"], "source_pack": "BIG5_LOW_QUALITY_REVISED_V0_3_NORMALIZED", "source_role": "backend_candidate_artifact"}, "summary_zh": "低置信状态下，越复杂、越外显、越长期的解释越需要收窄。", "target_registry_key": "state_scope_registry", "title_zh": "哪些内容要放轻", "version": "fap.big5.result_page_v2.content_asset_candidate.v0.3.normalized"}
{"applies_to": {"quality_status": ["low_confidence", "invalid", "insufficient"], "scale_code": ["BIG5_OCEAN"], "scope": ["low_quality"]}, "asset_id": "candidate_content_low_quality_non_blaming_boundary_v0_3", "asset_key": "low_quality_state.non_blaming_boundary.v0_3", "asset_kind": "content_asset", "asset_layer": "L7_result_state", "asset_type": "result_state", "asset_version": "v0_3", "avoid_when": [{"action": "suppress", "field": "scale_code", "operator": "not_equals", "value": "BIG5_OCEAN"}, {"action": "suppress", "field": "scope", "operator": "not_equals", "value": "low_quality"}], "body_quality": {"body_chars": 193, "cta_chars": 20, "has_action_layer": true, "has_boundary_layer": true, "has_editorial_leakage": false, "has_quality_layer": true, "has_retest_layer": false, "has_state_layer": true, "max_sentence_length": 42, "recalculated_by": "codex_low_quality_candidate_normalize_01", "rendered_preview_required": true, "sentence_count": 6, "short_body_chars": 24, "summary_chars": 23, "template_risk": "low"}, "body_zh": "当系统提示低置信时，它描述的是本次材料的可解释程度，而不是用户的认真程度、能力或人格。作答会受到时间、环境、疲劳、情绪和理解方式影响，任何一次测评都可能出现材料偏薄的情况。更合适的处理，是把提示看成阅读说明：哪些内容可以先看，哪些内容需要等更多信息再说。这样既保护用户，也保护报告本身不做过度解释。文案应避免责备语气，只说明如何更稳地阅读。这能让用户知道系统在收窄解释，而不是否定个人。", "can_combine_with": ["method_boundary_context", "retest_guidance", "safe_summary_context"], "cannot_combine_with": ["strong_personality_claim", "private_result_details", "ranking_claim", "high_stakes_language"], "copy_role": "degraded_state_boundary_candidate", "cta_zh": "把质量提示当作阅读说明，而不是自我评价。", "dedupe_group": "low_quality_state.non_blaming_boundary", "fallback_allowed": false, "module_key": "module_10_method_privacy", "production_use_allowed": false, "qa_status": "editorial_reviewed", "reading_mode": ["quick", "standard", "deep"], "ready_for_pilot": false, "ready_for_production": false, "ready_for_runtime": false, "render_surface": ["result_page", "pdf"], "repair_log_refs": [], "runtime_use": "staging_only", "safety_level": "degraded", "safety_tags": ["degraded_state", "non_blaming", "bounded_interpretation", "no_high_stakes_claim", "no_external_copy"], "scope": "low_quality", "section_key": "low_quality_state", "selection_priority": 91, "selection_specificity": 86, "short_body_zh": "这个提示不是在说你答得不好，而是在说明解释边界。", "slot_key": "low_quality.boundary.non_blaming", "source_trace": {"bfi_2_copy_used": false, "competitor_copy_used": false, "derived_from": ["06_low_quality_workpack", "scoring_norms_safe_summary", "editorial_handoff_prompt"], "external_copy_used": false, "forbidden_copy_sources_excluded": true, "source_labels": ["citation_only", "structure_reference_only"], "source_pack": "BIG5_LOW_QUALITY_REVISED_V0_3_NORMALIZED", "source_role": "backend_candidate_artifact"}, "summary_zh": "质量提示只说明材料厚度，不评价用户态度或人格。", "target_registry_key": "state_scope_registry", "title_zh": "质量提示不是责备", "version": "fap.big5.result_page_v2.content_asset_candidate.v0.3.normalized"}
{"applies_to": {"quality_status": ["low_confidence", "invalid", "insufficient"], "scale_code": ["BIG5_OCEAN"], "scope": ["low_quality"]}, "asset_id": "candidate_content_low_quality_retest_recommended_context_v0_3", "asset_key": "low_quality_state.retest_recommended_context.v0_3", "asset_kind": "content_asset", "asset_layer": "L7_result_state", "asset_type": "result_state", "asset_version": "v0_3", "avoid_when": [{"action": "suppress", "field": "scale_code", "operator": "not_equals", "value": "BIG5_OCEAN"}, {"action": "suppress", "field": "scope", "operator": "not_equals", "value": "low_quality"}], "body_quality": {"body_chars": 187, "cta_chars": 20, "has_action_layer": true, "has_boundary_layer": true, "has_editorial_leakage": false, "has_quality_layer": true, "has_retest_layer": true, "has_state_layer": true, "max_sentence_length": 60, "recalculated_by": "codex_low_quality_candidate_normalize_01", "rendered_preview_required": true, "sentence_count": 6, "short_body_chars": 24, "summary_chars": 27, "template_risk": "low"}, "body_zh": "重新作答适合出现在几种情况：你答得很赶，中途被打断，近期状态和长期状态差异很大，或者看完结果后发现很多描述都难以对应现实。重答的目的不是获得更好看的报告，而是让系统拥有更连贯的材料。建议不要在情绪很满、时间很碎或被外界持续打扰时重答。更好的方式，是留出一段完整时间，只按近期和长期都能解释的经验作答。这样得到的结果更适合进入深度阅读。重答前也可以先写下近期最典型的三个场景。", "can_combine_with": ["method_boundary_context", "retest_guidance", "safe_summary_context"], "cannot_combine_with": ["strong_personality_claim", "private_result_details", "ranking_claim", "high_stakes_language"], "copy_role": "degraded_state_retest_candidate", "cta_zh": "选择一个完整时间段，按真实经验重新作答。", "dedupe_group": "low_quality_state.retest_recommended_context", "fallback_allowed": false, "module_key": "module_10_method_privacy", "production_use_allowed": false, "qa_status": "editorial_reviewed", "reading_mode": ["quick", "standard", "deep"], "ready_for_pilot": false, "ready_for_production": false, "ready_for_runtime": false, "render_surface": ["result_page", "pdf"], "repair_log_refs": [], "runtime_use": "staging_only", "safety_level": "degraded", "safety_tags": ["degraded_state", "non_blaming", "bounded_interpretation", "no_high_stakes_claim", "no_external_copy"], "scope": "low_quality", "section_key": "low_quality_state", "selection_priority": 85, "selection_specificity": 85, "short_body_zh": "重答不是为了刷出更好结果，而是为了获得更稳材料。", "slot_key": "low_quality.retest.recommended", "source_trace": {"bfi_2_copy_used": false, "competitor_copy_used": false, "derived_from": ["06_low_quality_workpack", "scoring_norms_safe_summary", "editorial_handoff_prompt"], "external_copy_used": false, "forbidden_copy_sources_excluded": true, "source_labels": ["citation_only", "structure_reference_only"], "source_pack": "BIG5_LOW_QUALITY_REVISED_V0_3_NORMALIZED", "source_role": "backend_candidate_artifact"}, "summary_zh": "当作答被打断、节奏过快或前后差异较大时，重答更有意义。", "target_registry_key": "state_scope_registry", "title_zh": "什么时候值得重答", "version": "fap.big5.result_page_v2.content_asset_candidate.v0.3.normalized"}
